INSTALLER APO

-> n (https://github.com/tj/n) pour gÃ©rer les versions de NodeJS
$ git clone https://github.com/tj/n
$ cd n && sudo make install

-> node.js + npm
$ sudo n latest

-> update npm
$ sudo npm install -g npm@latest

-> grunt
$ sudo npm install -g grunt-cli

-> apo

$ git clone https://github.com/stromhalm/apo.git
$ cd apo
$ npm install

-> launch
$ grunt
